{"id": 2218, "genre": 1001, "title": "现如今，什么东西/做什么事能让你获得小剂量回血？", "description": "日常里，你都是从哪儿一点点找回自信的？（题图来自：视觉中国）", "record_count": 4814, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180309100949opYKZxAa3CRr26vm.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-03-12T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 269824, "content": "看电影", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1283542}, {"id": 270336, "content": "画一幅自己喜欢的画", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814937}, {"id": 269825, "content": "和我的家人相处聊天生活，会很快地回复状态", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1253178}, {"id": 269826, "content": "对喜欢的人说我喜欢你", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1283549}, {"id": 269827, "content": "向公司报销的款项打到了自己的银行账户上。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1262336}, {"id": 270852, "content": "夸我，谢谢", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1287078}, {"id": 269829, "content": "看书", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1128485}, {"id": 269830, "content": "做好吃的饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1134248}, {"id": 270598, "content": "学会一项新技能", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1285601}, {"id": 269831, "content": "辞职！", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1271021}, {"id": 269832, "content": "芝士", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1283570}, {"id": 269833, "content": "喂猫", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1250403}, {"id": 269834, "content": "打一下午游戏，看一部喜剧电影，和最爱的人逗逗嘴，或者画一张表现自己情感的设计图", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1233923}, {"id": 269835, "content": "看电影", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1283577}, {"id": 271115, "content": "爱\n\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1275045}, {"id": 273163, "content": "吃口糖，看个漫画。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1297980}, {"id": 269836, "content": "自己做点好吃的，尤其是挑战有难度的菜的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 942596}, {"id": 271117, "content": "当然是打扫卫生。超速度的在自己规定的时间内完成整个房间打扫，有种超厉害的满足感。打扫是可以高效而纯粹的做的一件事。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1289450}, {"id": 269838, "content": "大力打擊生活工作的小人??", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1283588}, {"id": 269839, "content": "买到超级喜欢的衣服，看书看电影刷美剧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 257518}, {"id": 269840, "content": "感受爱，创造爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1283592}, {"id": 269841, "content": "到开阔的江边走走，听着音乐，吹着江风，江边草色青青，很多都会变得简单许多", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 879075}, {"id": 269842, "content": "我买的虚拟币，股票都大涨", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711174}, {"id": 277522, "content": "充足的睡眠与我最爱的咖啡。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1324866}, {"id": 269843, "content": "捣鼓电脑\n疯狂研究黑苹果中", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1277555}, {"id": 269844, "content": "工作一点点交差", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 133687}, {"id": 269845, "content": "玩儿滑板(●°u°●)​ 」", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1283602}, {"id": 270613, "content": "钱，休息，玩", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1046395}, {"id": 269846, "content": "踢足球", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 464099}, {"id": 269847, "content": "玩PS", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 464099}, {"id": 269848, "content": "把作业写完，然后干点无用的事情，享受一种悠闲自在", "image": "img/option/option/20180312170036FrSKq2GEabfheQdy.jpg", "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1147878}, {"id": 270872, "content": "现在只有钱能让我觉得安稳，我就是这么俗气", "image": "img/option/option/20180316151838cNZ45Hoxt7z8sXEr.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 955239}, {"id": 269849, "content": "做爱爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1283605}, {"id": 269850, "content": "学习，每学到一项技能或者知识，以后少一句求人的话。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1242652}, {"id": 270362, "content": "在完成不了大目标时，会想一个小目标来马上实现，就会好很多", "image": "img/option/option/20180313230927ZpOcinLrBlbTVag1", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1284689}, {"id": 271386, "content": "吃东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1289203}, {"id": 269851, "content": "保持好的心情，乐观的生活态度。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1249286}, {"id": 271387, "content": "很好的身体状态", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1290312}, {"id": 269852, "content": "研究一下周围的环境，改造一下。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1249286}, {"id": 269853, "content": "出门骑车去吹风", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1239598}, {"id": 269856, "content": "出去散步，回母校和老师谈话", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1283613}, {"id": 270369, "content": "看看笑话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 22180}, {"id": 277281, "content": "抱抱我的狗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1112037}, {"id": 270371, "content": "拿下一个客户", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1284720}, {"id": 269860, "content": "在社交app上有人点赞加评论", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1258146}, {"id": 269863, "content": "迈开计划的第一步", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1230213}, {"id": 269864, "content": "跑步?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1282501}, {"id": 270633, "content": "吃学一种乐器去一个地方旅游", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1285743}, {"id": 270889, "content": "如果回血是指赚钱，那就是自己扫自己小号的支付宝红包再转给自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1287048}, {"id": 269866, "content": "不断用心理暗示提醒自己。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1264894}]}